OL,5, The co-founders of Hotel Chocolat will 
OL,6, each get #144m after agreeing to sell  
OL,7, the British business to Mars.          
OL,9,FThe US confectionery giant will pay    
OL,10,F#534m for the firm that Angus Thirlwell
OL,11,Fand Peter Harris set up in 1993.       
OL,13,FHotel Chocolat said the deal would     
OL,14,Fallow the brand to "grow further and   
OL,15,Ffaster", including overseas.           
OL,17,FThe company has had mixed success with 
OL,18,Fexpanding internationally and last year
OL,19,Fhad to shut down its five shops in the 
OL,20,FUS.                                    
